short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hides the Insert Video menu item on Google Slides.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is for Google Admins who need to remove the Insert Video option from Google Slides for those students who are supposed to have YouTube blocked due to discipline issues.
